      <phrase lang="zh_CN">概述</phrase>
    </title>

    <figure>
      <title>
        <phrase lang="en">An example of Make Seamless.</phrase>
        <phrase lang="de">
          Anwendungsbeispiel für das Filter <quote>Nahtlos machen</quote>
        </phrase>
        <phrase lang="fr">Un exemple de Rendre raccordable.</phrase>
        <phrase lang="it">
          Esempio di applicazione del filtro Rendi senza giunzioni
        </phrase>
        <phrase lang="ru">Пример фильтра <quote>Без швов</quote></phrase>
      </title>
      <mediaobject>
